# JAVA) Scanner class 이용해 입력하기

# JAVA 예시
```java
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main(){
    public static void main(String[] args){
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        String cmd = sc.nextLine();
    }
}
```

